trans-unit.source: Represents a cell in a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel" />.
The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition> to set the position of a child control in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> control.
trans-unit.target: 다음 예제에서는 사용 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다. <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition> 에서 자식 컨트롤의 위치를 설정 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For a full code listing, see [How to: Implement a Custom ToolStripRenderer](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/how-to-implement-a-custom-toolstriprenderer.md).
trans-unit.target: 전체 코드 목록을 참조 하십시오. [하는 방법: 사용자 지정 ToolStripRenderer 구현](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/how-to-implement-a-custom-toolstriprenderer.md)합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the column number of the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />.
The column number of the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> to test.

Specifies whether this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> contains the same row and column as the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />에 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />과 같은 행 및 열이 포함되어 있는지 여부를 지정합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="other" /> is a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> and has the same row and column as the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="other" />가 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />이고 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />과 같은 행 및 열을 가지고 있으면 <see langword="true" />를 반환하고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a hash code for this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />.

The result specifies whether the values of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition.Row" /> and <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition.Column" /> properties of the two <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> objects are equal.
trans-unit.target: 결과는 두 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition.Row" /> 개체의 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition.Column" /> 및 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> 속성 값이 같은지 여부를 지정합니다.
